### Health check (public, no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Should be 401 — confirms the auth gate is working
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects

### Create a project
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Project"
}

### List projects
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one project (copy the id from "create project" or "list projects" response)
@projectId = dUWuSn2rGe48VesvsBZy

GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a reference sample
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample 1",
  "text": "This is a short piece of writing that represents how I normally write. It's direct, a little informal, and gets to the point quickly without a lot of throat-clearing."
}

### Add a second sample (more samples = a better profile)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample 2",
  "text": "Another example of my writing — same voice, different topic. I tend to use short sentences and avoid unnecessary jargon when I can help it."
}

### List samples
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Generate the voice profile from all samples (LLM-backed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Read the cached profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Score a target draft against the profile (LLM-backed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/analyze
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "In light of the aforementioned circumstances, it is imperative that we proceed with the utmost caution and due diligence, taking into account all relevant stakeholders."
}

### Rewrite the target to match the voice profile (LLM-backed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/rewrite
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "target": "In light of the aforementioned circumstances, it is imperative that we proceed with the utmost caution and due diligence, taking into account all relevant stakeholders.",
  "instructions": "Make it punchier"
}

### --- Abuse-guard check: empty text should be 400 ---
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/samples
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Too big",
  "text": ""
}

### Delete a sample (grab a sampleId from the "list samples" response above)
@sampleId = BrSTXFc99mtZZ0QRLzLG
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}/samples/{{sampleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Cleanup ---

### Delete the whole project (and its samples/analyses)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Self-serve full account data deletion (GDPR-style) — wipes ALL your projects
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/account/data
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}